    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the spring greens are cooking, peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic </strong>and peel and finely dice your<strong> shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly if required</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>soy sauce </strong>and the<strong> chopped creamed coconut</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
