    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped shallot</strong>, <strong>ginger</strong> and <strong>garlic </strong>and<strong> </strong>cook for 2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>coconut stock </strong>and the <strong>jumbo king prawns </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 6-7 min or until the prawns are cooked through</p>",
