    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the<strong> cooked spring greens</strong> to the drained brown rice</p><p>Return the pot to a medium-low heat and cook for 1-2 min, gently stirring it together, or until the rice and spring greens are piping hot – this is your<strong> brown rice & greens</strong></p>",
